channel.description:
Note this is not DSPK.
The interface in which where you choose your classes For Dungeoneering. [IMG]http://i53.tinypic.com/2d11en8.jpg[/img]
The shop Interface Where you buy your Items [IMG]http://i56.tinypic.com/2d12sxt.jpg[/img]
Dungeoneering start (Must use ring of kinship) [IMG]http://i51.tinypic.com/xmssjp.jpg[/img]
Fullscreen [IMG]http://i55.tinypic.com/34rzssj.jpg[/img]
Ancient Prayers [IMG]http://i52.tinypic.com/16ixv6r.jpg[/img]
Hand cannon [IMG]http://i51.tinypic.com/ipqis3.jpg[/img]
Donator Options [IMG]http://i53.tinypic.com/5wa0eq.jpg[/img]
Other Features: - 1 Mini-Quest (Need To Complete To Start Dungeoneering To get the Ring Of Kinship) - Ancient Prayers Fully Working - Summoning - Dungeoneering (6 Floors) Not Finished You Can Do Rest Urself - All Minigames Work - Fixed a fair amount of glitches.
Hell of alot more i just can't remember :D
Downloads: Package Client+Source http://dl.dropbox.com/u/29457174/CautionX%20V1%20Package.rar
Note: This is not DSPK And It Is Just A BASE You can Improve this yourselves This was a Stock PI Source
This was the source originally: http://www.rune-server.org/runescape-development/rs2-server/downloads/308712-project-insanity-normal-pi-all-dupes-fixed.html
Credits; GabbeIsABaws (For FormationX Client) Jack (For the stock PI Source he released) And myself for Improving it. InsidiaX For NPC Spawn + Coords for dung. `Cody For dungeoneering shop sprites
For whoever wants 600+ Gameframe @ Client.java clientside find: [CODE]//switchGameframe(554); //sendFrame126("600+", 37058);[/CODE] Change it to: [CODE]switchGameframe(554); sendFrame126("600+", 37058);[/CODE]
[size=12pt]This was removed because someone claimed this wasn't my work when this is 100% My work The mod then asked me to prove it but I don't see how i could prove it It's not as if I have videos of me coding this?? They only proof I could possibly give Is friends that know I done this even then they could be lieing you never know so yea there is no way you can prove it's your work pretty Much this is 100% My work I can say that If anyone doesn't believe so then fuck off?[/size]
